'       > zthree= (100.0000,-1.000000) (200.0000,-1.000000) (30.00000,-1.000000)', &
'', &
'STANDARD', &
'  FORTRAN 77, KIND added in Fortran 90.', &
'', &
'SEE ALSO', &
'  o  AIMAG(3) - Imaginary part of complex number', &
'', &
