'  the intrinsic function INT to type integer with the kind type parameter of', &
'  the other.', &
'', &
'RESULT', &
'  If a bit is different at the same location in I and J the corresponding bit', &
'  in the result is 1, otherwise it is 0.', &
'', &
'EXAMPLES', &
