'', &
'DESCRIPTION', &
'  TRANSPOSE(3) transposes an array of rank two.', &
'', &
'  An array is transposed by interchanging the rows and columns of the given', &
'  matrix. That is, element (i,j) of the result has the value of element (j,i)', &
